STATE of North Carolina
v.
Janely Higuera CARDENAS No. 320P16 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 12, 2016. Ms. Ann B. Petersen, Mr. Johnny S. Gaskins, Attorneys at Law, For Cardenas, Janely Higuera. Mr. James R. Glover, Attorney at Law. Ms. Olga Vysotskaya de Brito, Assistant Attorney General, Ms. N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, For State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 29th of August 2016 by Defendant in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 8th of December 2016."
